metadata.name: Game On
metadata.description:
Our minds are more impressionable than we might like to admit. With the onslaught on information and digital exposure, we are more vulnerable to altering our thoughts and behaviour than ever before. 

It’s hard to disconnect from the noise, and get in touch with our innocent selves - if there is such a thing? Wouldn’t it be nice to go back to the start and find out.

Dimension 9000 x 9000 ( 300 DPI )
